CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 11, 1945, pg. 13, reads: "Deep Point - Atty. Wilbur Douglass, Frog member, drives home his point in his best 'jury manner,' as he talks with Frogs: Dr. Roy W. Taylor, Harry G. Washington, president of the group, and Dr. R. W. Dixon. - All Photos By Harris."
TitMainTitle: Atty. Wilbur Douglass, Dr. Roy W. Taylor, Harry G. Washington, and Dr. Reginald W. Dixon gathered on bench outside of South Park lodge for FROGS picnic
